{
  "stem": "1857.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 358.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now this was-- if you were not there, you don't realize what it meant to get a pair of glasses in Czechoslovakia from Poland, what Mrs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Schindler arranged for.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Now we were there for a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a friend of mine, who was from my school, and was very close to Schindler, because he-- he was Schindler's chauffeur, told to me that they have a group they created underground, that a Czech underground was providing weapons for them-- whether I want to join.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, yes I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He talked to Schindler about me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Schindler knew all about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Schindler put me into electrical transformer, where there were huge bails of electrical wires.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And under those wires, they were hiding the weapons and ammunition.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my job was to make sure that the German foreman in the transformer would not get close to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But every time he got close to it, my heart was stopping.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And the whole thing took a couple of weeks that I was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the greatest thing that Schindler did is when the news came-- and this was around February, the beginning of February of 1945-- that some boxcars were abandoned on a siding, four boxcars with Jews.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this was a very severe winter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Schindler went by himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he found out that there were Jewish people there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he dispatched two trucks with people-- I was among them-- in order to open the boxcars and get the people out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The doors of those boxcars were frozen, completely frozen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we couldn't open it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So he sent back one truck to bring torches.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we heat up with torches those doors and we opened.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
